ller','Malayalam','Amal Neerad','R.J. Murugan, Amal Neerad, Ravishankar P.T., Devadath Shaji','Abin Thomas Biju, Amal Neerad, Anwar Rasheed, Arun Unnikrishnan','Sushin Shyam','Anend C. Chandran','Vivek Harshan'),('#Home',8.8,'Oliver Twist (Indrans) wants to be tech-savvy and become a better companion to his two sons, who spend more time on their phones than with their loved ones.',158,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNWU1ZmNlYTctYmY1My00ZDlmLTk3M2EtZDcxY2E1ZGU0N2YzXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTI1NDAzMzM0.jpg',2021,'Drama','Malayalam','Rojin Thomas','Rojin Thomas','Vijay Babu, Vinay Babu','Rahul Subrahmanian','Neil D\'Cuncha','Prejish Prakash'),('Karannakaran',NULL,'Everyone knows it\'s impossible to kill Mitran but no-one knows why. Thugs Christy and team are promised a huge amount of money to kill Mitran. They find out that Mitran somehow always knows the plans to kill him. Meanwhile, Mitran gets his land mafia exposed by activists Naveen and Manju through an article. Mitran kills Manju\'s brother Sandeep. Manju and Naveen go on the run from Mitran\'s thugs with their driver (Indrans). Christy and team plan to kill Mitran from his gym backfires. Mitran kills Jimmy by making him drink the poison that they made for him. Everyone joins forces to kill Mitran. They learn that everyone fails at killing Mitran because of Mitran\'s mother Sarojini who gets a feeling that something bad is going to happen to her son whenever someone plans to kill him. She calls and warns him immediately. Manju decides to go to Mitran\'s mother\'s house to confirm this. She bonds with Mitran\'s mother and gets life advice from her. Mitran\'s mother gets a vision that someone will kill him from the elevator of the shopping mall he wants to buy. She tries to stop him, but Mitran will stop at nothing to get what he wants. How will Stephen\'s murder team kill Mitran when his mother has already seen the murder that will happen?',NULL,NULL,2021,'Crime, Thriller','Malayalam','Vishnu Chandran','Vishnu Vinod',NULL,'Amritesh Vijayan','Bipin','Rajeesh'),('Mohan Kumar Fans',5.5,'Mohan Kumar is an ex-superstar, and Krishnan Unni is his greatest fan and also his driver. The film depicts the lengths that Krishnan Unni and Mohan Kumar\'s family and friends go to, in order to keep him happy--no matter what it takes.',126,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNDVjZWYyMDktMGViYi00NzlkLWFiMDctYWU3NmM4MzVhODg1XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMjkxNzQ1NDI@.jpg',2021,'Drama','Malayalam','Jis Joy','Bobby, Jis Joy, Sanjay','Santhosh Krishnan, Justin Stephen, Listin Stephen, Naveen P. Thomas','William Francis, Prince George','Bahul Ramesh','Ratheesh Raj'),('Hasyam',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMDdlZGE3M2QtNGZjMi00MjM3LWJkM2EtMjg0ZDQwNzY5MzEwXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMzQ5Njc3NzU@.jpg',2021,'Drama','Malayalam','Jayaraaj',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Vinod Illampally',NULL),('Chakkappazham',7.3,'Follows the life of Uthaman and his family.',NULL,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMzI0YWVhMWQtZjQzNS00NDk4LWJmNWItZjkyODI0OWVmZjJjXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNTEwMTY1OTQ@.jpg',2020,'Comedy','Malayalam',NULL,'Shameer Khan',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('Varane Avashyamund',6.9,'Neena is a French teacher and single parent to Nikitha (Nikki), who works at a bank and is obsessed with the concept of arranged marriage. Their lives change when a retired army man, Major Unnikrishnan, and another young man, fondly named Fraud, come to stay at the apartment. The lives of these four people, their pasts and their emotions, all crash into one another under the same roof.',145,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BZWE3MzIyMDUtYTMxMy00YjMyLWIyZGMtNjg2NGZiODU1ZDZiXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMjkxNzQ1NDI@.jpg',2020,'Comedy, Drama, Romance','Malayalam','Anoop Sathyan','Anoop Sathyan, Sairam Vishwa','Harris Desom, Dulquer Salmaan','Alphons Joseph','Mukesh Muraleedharan','Toby John'),('Ulta',7.1,'Story of a fictional town called Ponnapuram, where all the women are self-sufficient and trained to handle any situation. Their world is put to the tes