pted by the Police Commissioner (Om Shivpuri). Joseph, now known as Tripathi, comes to know that Ravi is Ghanshyam\'s son, and devices a scheme that will bring certain death to Ghanshyam and his family.',150,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BZGE0OWRjZjUtNDExZC00YThmLWIwMDQtMTI2MjA2ODUyNjNmXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyOTIzODUxMjk@.jpg',1982,'Action, Crime, Drama, Family','Hindi','Mohan Segal',NULL,'Jawaharlal B. Bafana, Vasant Doshi, C.D. Mehta, B.N. Shah','Rahul Dev Burman',NULL,NULL),('Jeeo Aur Jeene Do',4.9,NULL,NULL,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BZDVkZjc1MjctNDdmZi00OGU1LWFjMzgtNTgyM2E3MjI2MzNmXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyODE5NzE3OTE@.jpg',1982,'Action, Drama','Hindi','Shyam Ralhan',NULL,'Ratan Mohan','Laxmikant Shantaram Kudalkar, Pyarelal Ramprasad Sharma','Sudarshan Nag',NULL),('Sitam',2.9,'The story is about an Advertising professional Raj who is a womanizer. What happens when he refuses to tie the knot claiming that he will only settle for a homely, decent girl.',NULL,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNDA0ZWI2MmUtODg4MS00MWMxLWJiMDAtY2Y5Y2QwODBjNmRlL2ltYWdlL2ltYWdlXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNzAwMDk4ODc@.jpg',2005,'Drama','Hindi','Partho Ghosh','Mehmood Ali','Kamal Rashid Khan','Nikhil, Vinay','Nazme Hasan Khan',NULL),('Anokha Bandhan',6.2,'When Annapurna mother was dying her mother in law takes a promise from her that she will take care of her son Ram as his son. After sometimes of Annapurna mother in law death she got a new healthy baby. The also her love and affection was much towards Ram. Ram and Annapurna\'s child live like real brother. But their happiness was not too much long when Annapurna\'s mother came to her house who does want that Annapurna should hate ram. Will Annapurna will hate Ram or their live will be same like that.',134,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMDRhZjMwNjUtZWMwMS00MmE0LTg5NDctNmJjYTRjMmI2ZjA4XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMzU0NzkwMDg@.jpg',1982,'Drama','Hindi','Mehul Kumar','Asad Bhopali, Saratchandra Chatterjee, Bharat Dave, Nida Fazli, Yogesh','Ra