hat the Rani had colluded with the local money-lenders and has taken over their land and property. Then the police arrest Chandrashekhar on the complaint filed by the Rani on the charge of stealing from his former employer. On the verge of losing her ill son, Laxmi, now penniless, must now find out why Rani Padmavati has taken it upon herself to ruin this family,',NULL,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BOWU0MjMxMDYtYzg0MC00ODc5LWIyZTctMTQyMjliNjM0OTA3XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyODE5NzE3OTE@.jpg',1975,'Drama, Family','Hindi','Adurthi Subba Rao','Inder Raj Anand, Prabhakar Reddy','A.S.R. Anjaneyulu, Vadye Subhanandu','Naushad',NULL,NULL),('Ya Sukhano Ya',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BODE1N2M0YzEtNTcwNy00ZWYxLWIzNDctYTY4NzY3NTA1NDM5XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyOTE3NDkxMDM@.jpg',2007,'Family','Marathi',NULL,'Shirish Latkar',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('Rani Aur Lalpari',6.8,'Rani is a child who is being brought up by her mother, Kamla, as her dad has gone out of the town on business. Both mother and daughter live with their cruel and selfish relatives. One day Kamla gets the news that her husband is returning, and she is overjoyed. This joy turns to sorrow when she finds out that he has passed away in an accident. Shortly, thereafter she too passes away, leaving poor Rani at the hands of the cruel relatives. Rani loves her parents, as they are her world, and she undertakes a journey into the netherworld to try and bring her parents back to life. This movie also features the story of Cinderella and Gulliver\'s Travels, in two songs.',135,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMzlmODIwNjEtYWIzZS00YzU0LWI4YmYtNGUzMGQyZTY0MThhXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNDQwOTAzNw@@.jpg',1975,'Drama, Family, Fantasy, Musical','Hindi','Ravikant Nagaich',NULL,'Hari Prasad Nagaich, Rani Nagaich','Vasant Desai','Ravikant Nagaich',NULL),('Kora Kagaz',7.2,'Archana, an educated daughter of retired principal loves Professor Sukhesh. This love born out of intellectual impact is supported by the fond hopes of her father that leads to matrimonial alliance. Archana\'s mother is of a different class with materialistic notions of life and she too unwillingly gives her consent to the marriage. Seeds of marital love have not yet flowered into sweet joys of wedlock when whims and ego\'s of Archana and Sukhesh start clashing. Though a dutiful loving wife of a sweet husband, Archana is very much the daughter of her mother, who with all good intentions intervenes in the day to day life of the couple. Understanding leads to misunderstandings and the lovers start misinterpreting each other\'s sentiments. This ultimately leads to break in marriage - hence the ultimate- eventual separation. Kora Kagaz answers the struggle of intellectual lovers who find it difficult to enjoy marital bliss. The film is a lesson in both love and marriage.',125,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNTA3NGQ5NmUtZTYwYy00YThmLWE2YjAtNzhhODdjYTRmMjgyXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyODE5NzE3OTE@.jpg',1974,'Drama, Musical, Family, Romance','Hindi','Anil Ganguly','M.G. Hashmat, Sisir Misra, Ashutosh Mukherjee, Surendra Shailaj','Sanat Kothari','Anandji Veerji Shah, Kalyanji Veerji Shah','Bipin Gajjar','Waman B. Bhosle, Guru Dutt'),('Naya Nasha',4.7,'Reena lives a very wealthy lifestyle with her businessman dad, socialite mom, and widower paternal grandfather in a mansion. She studies in college, is very bored, and joins protesting students who are agitating against rising college fees. She has a crush on their family doctor, Samar Chowdhary. She goes on a date with him to a club and falls for the club\'s singer, Sharad, who rejects her. Still bored, she gets friendly with Kitty, who in turn introduces her to Rana, and from thence on Reena gets hooked on drugs and starts coming home late at night. Her grandfather notices this and tells her dad, who in turn confronts her, and convinces her to get married to Samar. The marriage does take place but Reena is unable to keep away from drugs, and refuses any treatment. She gets pre